  %2 = shufflevector <8 x i8> %1, <8 x i8> <i8 0, i8 9, i8 1, i8 9, i8 2, i8 9, i8 3, i8 9>, <8 x i32> <i32 0, i32 8, i32 2, i32 10, i32 4, i32 12, i32 6, i32 14>
